00:11:18,226 --> 00:11:26,910
This is a meeting of the Medford City Council Public Health and Community Safety Committee, May 20th, 6 p.m.

6
00:11:27,650 --> 00:11:41,696
The purpose of this meeting is to discuss the yearly report about surveillance that's conducted by the police department and the parking department.

7
00:11:45,411 --> 00:11:47,934
