15
00:12:29,266 --> 00:12:51,781
What is frustrating is when activist groups or public organizations or grassroots organizations from Medford ask me as the chair of this committee to follow up with the police department.

16
00:12:54,232 --> 00:13:06,460
And I do that three weeks after the report was due, send a message to the chief of police asking about the report, and do not receive the report for six more weeks.

17
00:13:08,242 --> 00:13:15,187
Not only did I not receive the report for six weeks after that, but I did not receive a reply to my first message.

18
00:13:16,614 --> 00:13:23,775
I did not, after the second message, a week later, I received a reply that said, I will call you tomorrow.

19
00:13:24,076 --> 00:13:26,536
Did not receive a call the following day.

20
00:13:27,676 --> 00:13:35,818
The third time I reached out, it was a text message expressing frustration, saying, we're having the committee meeting.

21
00:13:36,658 --> 00:13:39,859
This was now May, two months after the report was due.

22
00:13:40,839 --> 00:13:45,620
I said, we're having the committee meeting, and the meeting's going to be about how you didn't do the report unless you do the report.

23
00:13:47,354 --> 00:13:54,200
And then a fourth time, I sent an email and cc'd the mayor, and then the report appeared.

24
00:13:55,961 --> 00:14:00,645
