29
00:14:24,205 --> 00:14:31,588
You can't ask questions to somebody who is not in attendance at a meeting and is not on Zoom.

30
00:14:31,608 --> 00:14:32,829
So that's problematic.

31
00:14:33,529 --> 00:14:37,511
We do, however, have the department head from the parking department.

32
00:14:37,551 --> 00:14:45,634
The parking department also has some surveillance that happens for

33
