enforcement of parking laws, parking rules.

34
00:14:53,525 --> 00:15:01,289
I didn't remind our department head, again, the issue is not that things slip our minds that are due once a year.

35
00:15:02,969 --> 00:15:04,390
If it wasn't part of the

36
