50
00:16:14,655 --> 00:16:19,619
The highest officer of law enforcement in Medford is the chief of police.

51
00:16:20,439 --> 00:16:22,221
Does how make it make sense?

52
00:16:24,569 --> 00:16:28,993
I'm feeling extremely frustrated by the series of events that led us here.

53
00:16:30,575 --> 00:16:45,570
If we could have had a conversation civilly in this room this evening, I wouldn't have said all of this in a public meeting, but I feel that it's necessary to explain that, you know, we're not

54
00:16:46,317 --> 00:16:58,984
In fifth grade, and we're not talking about spelling homework, we're talking about the legal requirements of an ordinance written by the legislative body of the city of Medford, people who were elected by the people of Medford.

55
00:16:59,064 --> 00:17:01,906
So I don't think this is appropriate.

56
00:17:02,286 --> 00:17:04,588
I don't think any of this should have occurred.

57
00:17:06,829 --> 00:17:11,432
That being said, today we received

58
00:17:12,697 --> 00:17:14,818
a report from the parking department.

