240
00:31:47,658 --> 00:31:48,318
Councillor Sang.

241
00:31:50,819 --> 00:31:51,239
Thank you.

242
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:56,301
This is not, as said, this is not about parking, but about police.

243
00:31:59,062 --> 00:32:05,364
This is an ordinance that community members have worked a really long time, over years,

244
00:32:06,338 --> 00:32:09,660
to draft, to pass, to advocate for.

245
00:32:11,322 --> 00:32:18,126
And I think the purpose of the ordinance is something that is really valuable.

246
00:32:18,687 --> 00:32:27,413
That the idea that in a world where modern surveillance is so prevalent and is so everywhere in our lives,

247
00:32:28,870 --> 00:32:37,096
And yet, we're so unaware of it that the public should have some control over surveillance.

248
00:32:37,216 --> 00:32:39,117
I think it's a really important idea.

249
00:32:43,082 --> 00:32:53,506
I think a lot of us share the frustrations that Chair Lozano has expressed at the start of the meeting and throughout the meeting.

250
00:32:54,746 --> 00:33:03,570
