294
00:37:48,733 --> 00:37:51,815
of Medford asking questions about this very topic.

295
00:37:51,995 --> 00:37:56,737
It is frustrating to be here and not be able to ask them at all.

296
00:37:56,997 --> 00:38:07,562
So I appreciate you, Vice President Lazaro, and the work of trying to reach out and get this scheduled and get a report done and put together.

297
00:38:07,662 --> 00:38:08,963
