00:38:34,126 --> 00:38:38,487
Okay, so we have a motion on the floor from Councilor Seng.

302
00:38:38,547 --> 00:38:43,869
Councilor, would you mind repeating what that motion was?

303
00:38:44,929 --> 00:38:55,312
Just a motion to keep this, to schedule another meeting with MPD present and to keep the paper in committee.

304
00:38:55,772 --> 00:38:59,413
And we should probably have the motion include inviting

305
00:39:00,687 --> 00:39:12,149
Director McDermott as well, so that we have time to review the report and ask any follow-up questions, though we did have a pretty robust discussion.

306
00:39:12,210 --> 00:39:16,670
It's still kind of, if possible, would be nice to do that.

307
00:39:16,831 --> 00:39:17,051
OK.

308
00:39:17,951 --> 00:39:21,111
Given that Matt's online, maybe you can add a journey to it.

309
00:39:21,852 --> 00:39:22,392
Oh, yes.

310
00:39:22,632 --> 00:39:23,532
Just to save us time.

311
00:39:25,253 --> 00:39:25,474
Great.

