00:39:48,605 --> 00:39:49,505
Councilor Scott Petley?

318
00:39:50,186 --> 00:39:50,406
Yes.

319
00:39:52,099 --> 00:39:52,760
Councilor Singh?

320
00:39:53,021 --> 00:39:53,221
Yes.

